survey_response.review_text:
Dr Naik is very good at her work. Dr Deval is very friendly , calm and always smiling. She explained me everything in detail and did a painless treatment. The clinic is well maintained and hygienic. 
Thank you doctor!!

Harshit, my 2.5 yrs son then now he is 8, was going through unberable toth pains, he used to cry in middle of the his sleep, in such conditions Dr. Deval has precisely digonised the issue, and carried very careful and successful treatment for a boy of such a young age. Almost most of the teeth of my son was having issue, out of which 4 teeth needed root canaling and then capping. My was relifed from the pains is was under going, just b'cos proper diagonisis Dr. Deval had done and giving us confidence to take a decision for this treatment of our son at this young age.
Now my son is 8 and got new teeths, still 2 caps yet come out. 
Lot Thanks to Dr. Deval

***** ** *** *** *** ****** ****** ************** I went her to show my broken tooth for which she recommended the Root Canal. I opted for the same and she did it in single setting. I asked her as how could she do it in single setting to which she said, the tooth wasn't infected so she could do it in single setting. During the Root canal treatment she was in very much hurry , I asked her about that too to which she said she is like that every time. She completed the Root Canal and put the temporary Cement which came out in just an hour. I was very much worried by then as I had got the Root Canal done in single setting and my Jaws have started paining as the anaesthesia effect was going away. It pained for two days (mys mistake too as I did not take the Pain Killer). But then Overall it wasn't a great experience. I consulted another Doctor for further treatment.  *** ** **** *********** **** **** He explained me all the problems in detail. I also found her charges exorbitant. She said filling of a tooth would cost 2500, Root Canal 3500, consultation 300 and crowns 6000 to 8000.

Both the Doctor are cordial and very professional.  I visited the doctor for my tooth straightening and the cleanup.  Dr. Deval explained the problem and all the possible options available to fix the problem and finally concluded on going with the root canal and Zirconia crowns for my front teeth.  The treatment was carried very well, and I am very happy with the result and would recommend others to visit this clinic for all dental problems.  Overall satisfied with the clinic and the doctors, clinic is very well maintained and have good hygiene standards.  All the Covid protocols were adhered and patients were attended only on appointment basis
